---
title: Honey-Garlic Chicken Bowls with Peppers and Carrots
description: Honey-garlic and soy sauce balance each other out in this easy stir-fry! Tender chicken and wholesome veggies are cloaked in this sweet and salty sauce, then served over fluffy jasmine rice.
